Description: 
 Tools to calculate statistical power, minimum detectable effect size,
 and constrained optimal sample allocation for main and moderator effects
 in various randomized controlled trials (individual- or cluster-level randomization, and single- or multi-site),
 and for main effects in various regression discontinuity designs (individual- or cluster-level discontinuity, and single- or multi-site)
 with continuous outcomes.
URL: https://github.com/metinbulus/PowerUpR
